Turkish Natural-Gas Provider Increases Prices Up to 14% on Lira

-- B y   E m r e   P e k e r   a n d   A l i   B e r a t   M e r i c
-- 
2011-10-01T08:13:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-01/turkish-natural-gas-provider-increases-prices-up-to-14-on-lira.html
Botas Boru Hatlari Ile Petrol Tasima
AS said it will raise residential natural-gas prices by 12.3
percent to 14.3 percent, citing increases on international
markets and the declining value of the Turkish lira.  The new pricing will take effect today, the Ankara-based
gas distributor said. Fees for industrial clients will go up
13.7 percent to 14.3 percent, Botas said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
